    "comment_id" : 50485944,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "If you want to exit a method with <code>System.exit(0)</code> you need to follow it with a return or throw statement to compile, and I like to use <code>throw null</code> for this."
  } ],
